{"tid":329874,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"諗住係Youtube 開個channel 教DSE ECON,唔知大家有無趣興睇?","createTime":"2017-07-20T16:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T12:29:17.000Z","uid":29740,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ded15e4c35010815a11359e82bf00a95f2f6796a","tid":329874,"uid":29740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T16:59:32.000Z","msg":"如果大家係預我教大家咩ECON 神技,咩ECON 必殺技既話可以上一頁<br />\n無論DSE ECON又好,AL ECON 又好, CE ECON 又好.<br />\n其實考既內容都唔係太深. <br />\n所以理論上係夠時間讀識晒成個課程<br />\n唔計背野個D,其實DSE ECON 只係將一啲ECON 理倫套用返係唔同題目<br />\n如果你識晒D理論,同運用返係唔同題目到,其實最少都有5*<br />\n<br />\n大家有無咩覺得特別難既TOPICS, 如果有既話我可以先拍.<br />\n但我應該會10月頭先放第一條片,係出年DSE ECON 考試前會拍晒<br />\n<br />\n最後各位巴絲一定會問,你邊位?憑咩教ECON,一陣教錯晒點算.<br />\n所以都係利申返,本人HK ALEVEL ECON 拎A. 大學讀ECON FIRST HON. <br />\n不是係香港讀大學<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過如果大家無興趣既話都無謂曬大家時間<br />\n唔知大家有咩興趣?"},{"pid":"f83f680b604d30148e159be27427e43b00b297c7","tid":329874,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:00:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d988407dd0e74310f6beed540441b905381b376","tid":329874,"uid":29740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:01:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">曬時間</span><img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XBc6b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXBc6b.png&h=88eefc41&s={SIZE}\" /> <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">嘥時間</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XBkTp.md.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXBkTp.md.png&h=f6a6fc4a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n更正返.係嘥<br />\n多謝提點"},{"pid":"28206a346ec5b22550657020404aa3a2447d3734","tid":329874,"uid":129288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T12:29:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">曬時間</span><img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XBc6b.png\" data-thumbnail-